        citations:
            - citation-twoiaf-targaryen
        confidence: high
        status: accepted
        notes: "Verified against TWOIAF, The Targaryen Kings section (Band of Nine). The fifth and last Blackfyre Pretender, slain by Ser Barristan Selmy. Source text: MAELYS BLACKFYRE, THE MONSTROUS: Captain of the Golden Company, named for his grotesquely huge torso and arms, fearsome strength, and savage nature. A second head grew from his neck, no bigger than a fist."
