        citations:
            - citation-twoiaf-targaryen
        confidence: high
        status: accepted
        notes: "Verified against TWOIAF, The Targaryen Kings section. Source text: Maelys the Monstrous was the fifth and last of the Blackfyre Pretenders; with his death, the curse that Aegon the Unworthy had inflicted on the Seven Kingdoms by giving his sword to his bastard son was finally ended."
